{{Quote|Now, time for the soup. Jabba likes a good beetle broth. He calls it stew, but actually it's broth. We need beetle carcasses. For flavor I'd say about 15. Rock or cave beetles. Either one.|[[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]]|<ref name="SWG:JPP">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Jabba's Palace : Porcellus|Tatooine}}</ref>}}
'''Beetle broth''' was a soup-like meal made of [[rock beetle]]s or [[cave beetle]]s on the planet [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was a favorite meal of local crime boss [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]], who called it ''beetle stew'' although his cook, [[Porcellus/Legends|Porcellus]], insisted that is was a broth and not a stew. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], Porcellus hired a [[Spacer/Legends|spacer]] in order to kill several rock beetles and bring him their carcasses to cook a beetle broth for Jabba.<ref name="SWG:JPP" />

